general.name: DRQ_sup
general.short: migrated from old datamodel - needs update
general.description:
Along with the primary DR12Q catalog, serendipitous quasars were identified, as documented in PÃ¢ris et al. (2015).

This webpage documents the format of the DR12Q_sup.fits and DR12Q_supbad.fits files. The first list of quasars was serendipitously identified in the course of various tests of the DR12Q superset definition. The second list was identified in plates that did not reach survey quality and were not re-observed later. Individual fits files are available for these quasars.
general.naming_convention: migration: not in database. Needs update

hdu0.name: PRIMARY
hdu0.description:
The data in this primary HDU consists of bytes which
comprise a VOTABLE document.
The VOTable describes the metadata of the table contained
in the following BINTABLE extension.
Such a BINTABLE extension can be used on its own as a perfectly
good table, but the information from this HDU may provide some
useful additional metadata.
